=== Pronunciation ===
[[Category:Hebrew language]]
רדה / râdâh / raw-daw'
=== Etymology ===

A primitive root; 
=== Verb ===
to [[tread]] down, that is, [[subjugate]]; specifically to crumble off: - (come to, make to) have dominion, prevail against, [[reign]], (bear, make to) rule, (-r, over), take.
